OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784657907
OL,3,CStephen Graham honoured with LIPA
OL,4,Ccompanionship from Sir Paul McCartney
OL,6,FStephen Graham has received a
OL,7,Fcompanionship from Sir Paul McCartney
OL,8,Fat the Liverpool Institute for
OL,9,FPerforming Arts graduation ceremony.
OL,11,FThe actor has won a Bafta, Emmy,
OL,12,FGolden Globe and Critic's Choice Award
OL,13,Ffor his starring role in the series
OL,14,FAdolescence.
OL,16,FHe is now one of five leading figures
OL,17,Ffrom creative industries to have been
OL,18,Fawarded with the LIPA companionship
OL,19,Fduring a ceremony at the Liverpool
OL,20,FExperience Campus on 21 July.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
