PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784657907
OL,3,CStephen Graham honoured with LIPA
OL,4,Ccompanionship from Sir Paul McCartney
OL,6,FBorn and raised on Merseyside, Graham
OL,7,Fis best known for starring in
OL,8,Fproductions including This Is England,
OL,9,FBoardwalk Empire, Line of Duty, Peaky
OL,10,FBlinders, Boiling Point and A Thousand
OL,11,FBlows.
OL,13,FBafta award winning actress and write
OL,14,FCathy Tyson - who grew up in Liverpool
OL,15,F- also received the honour, having
OL,16,Ffounded the Brown Girls Films
OL,17,Fproduction company which has been
OL,18,Fbehind productions including Blue
OL,19,FLights, Dune: Prophecy and Ride or Die.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
