OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784657907
OL,3,CStephen Graham honoured with LIPA
OL,4,Ccompanionship from Sir Paul McCartney
OL,6,FProducer Lynette Howell Taylor - who
OL,7,Fis also from Liverpool and graduated
OL,8,Fwith a management degree from LIPA in
OL,9,F2000 - was also among those awarded
OL,10,Fthe honour, having produced more than
OL,11,F25 feature films including A Star is
OL,12,FBorn.
OL,14,FNow President of the Academy of Motion
OL,15,FPicture Arts and Sciences ` the
OL,16,Forganisation behind the Oscars, Howell
OL,17,FTaylor said: "The foundation for my
OL,18,Fcareer was built at LIPA. It was the
OL,19,Ffirst time I felt truly seen for my
OL,20,Fpassion and abilities.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784657907
OL,3,CStephen Graham honoured with LIPA
OL,4,Ccompanionship from Sir Paul McCartney
OL,6,F"The teaching staff encouraged,
OL,7,Fsupported and pushed me to explore my
OL,8,Fcapabilities.
OL,10,F"I owe so much to LIPA's founders Mark
OL,11,FFeatherstone-Witty and Sir Paul
OL,12,FMcCartney for creating a truly
OL,13,Fcreative and cross discipline
OL,14,Fenvironment where both artists and
OL,15,Fthose that enable and work with
OL,16,Fartists can thrive.
OL,18,F"Being honoured this way means a
OL,19,Ftremendous amount to me and my
OL,20,Fgratitude is endless."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
