PN,36505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784657907
OL,3,CStephen Graham honoured with LIPA
OL,4,Ccompanionship from Sir Paul McCartney
OL,6,FA LIPA Companionship is awarded in
OL,7,Frecognition of outstanding achievement
OL,8,Fin the creative industries and a
OL,9,Fsignificant contribution to student
OL,10,Flearning.
OL,12,FThe companionships were bestowed by
OL,13,FLIPA's founding patron, Sir Paul, in a
OL,14,Fceremony that celebrated the
OL,15,Fachievements of more than 400
OL,16,Fgraduating students from 28 countries.
OL,18,FLIPA's principal and chief executive
OL,19,Fofficer professor Sean McNamara said:
OL,20,F"This is a milestone graduation for us.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784657907
OL,3,CStephen Graham honoured with LIPA
OL,4,Ccompanionship from Sir Paul McCartney
OL,6,F"As we mark our 30th anniversary and
OL,7,Fconfer our first LIPA degrees, today
OL,8,Fis a celebration of creativity and
OL,9,Fcollaboration.
OL,11,F"Our graduating class of 2026 leaves
OL,12,Fhere as artists, innovators and
OL,13,Fleaders with the skills, vision and
OL,14,Fconfidence to shape the creative and
OL,15,Fcultural industries.
OL,17,F"It is fitting that we celebrate their
OL,18,Fachievements alongside the outstanding
OL,19,Fartists, producers and managers who
OL,20,Fjoin us today as LIPA Companions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784657907
OL,3,CStephen Graham honoured with LIPA
OL,4,Ccompanionship from Sir Paul McCartney
OL,6,F"We are immensely proud of them all
OL,7,Fand look forward to seeing the future
OL,8,Fthey create together."
OL,10,FLIPA was founded in 1996 by Sir Paul
OL,11,Fand Mark Featherstone-Witty.
OL,13,FIt occupies the former Liverpool
OL,14,FInstitute school, which the former
OL,15,Fattended with his Beatles bandmate
OL,16,FGeorge Harrison, alongside the
OL,17,Fneighbouring Liverpool Art College,
OL,18,Fwhere John Lennon studied.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
